<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٣)</span> وَالتَّمْيِيزُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَزَمَنُهَا:</span> أَوَّلُ العِبَادَةِ، أَوْ قُبَيْلَهَا بِيَسِيرٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأَرْكَانُ الصَّلَاةِ أَرْبَعَةَ عَشَرَ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
